PySide is provided with an extensive set of network classes to support both
client-based and server side network programming.

These examples demonstrate the fundamental aspects of network programming
with PySide.


The example launcher provided with PySide can be used to explore each of the
examples in this directory.

Documentation for these examples can be found via the Tutorial and Examples
link in the main Side documentation.


Finding the PySide Examples and Demos launcher
==============================================

On Windows:

The launcher can be accessed via the Windows Start menu. Select the menu
entry entitled "Examples and Demos" entry in the submenu containing PySide.

On all platforms:

The source code for the launcher can be found in the examples/demos/qtdemo
directory in the PySide package.
